name: chapter II : 𝖘𝖔𝖚𝖑𝖘
description:
am I lost? the cries of the walking people, those who had dark circles in their eyes, not even the tears are enough to return, we do not know it will be happiness or sadness? My eyes are going blind from so much light, from so many souls , I only hear your heartbreaking song, a meow, a purr, a moan, that makes me forget all my memories.
A soul whispered to me that in 49 days we will return to the post-earth, where will we return? I know it's my seventh day and I don't know where I am.-
